  "description": "A new whimsical delight from the company that brought you the smash hit, OFFICIAL HOLDOVER show, FOR SCIENCE! ★★★★★ Edmonton Journal, ★★★★★ Vue Mag, ★★★★★ Fringe2Fringe. Sandra and Sabrina do their darndest to find Forever Foot Friends for lost and lonely single socks. Be part of the solution! Learn more at www.sockrescue.ca.",
